      "text": "Uhda Behrni bija:\nPeerez/ Ezrons un Kar-\nnus/ un Urs/ un So-\nbals.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Reajus Sobala Dehls\ndsemdinaja Jakatu. Un Jakats\ndsemdtuaja Akimaju/ un Lāādu/\nschee irr to/ Zaregatiteru Raddi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee irr no ta Tehwa\nGetam/ Jesreēls/ Jesmus un\nJedbas/ un winna Mahtai bija\nAziełponi Wahrda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Pannēls bija Gedora\nTehws/ un Cesers bija Usus\nTehws. Schee irr Ura Behrni\nCewrata Pirindsfimmuschā/ Bet-\nlema Tehwa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Asuram Tekons Teh-\nwain bija divi Seewas/ Ellean/\nun Naēra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Naēra dsemdēja tam\nAkusu/ un Ewerv/ un Temnu/\nun Akastarn. Schee irr Naē-\nras Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Elleas Behrni bija:\nZerets/ Jezcars un Etnans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Koz dsemdinaja Anu-\nbu un Azobehn/ un tohs Rad-\ndus Nāreēta Aruma Dehla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jaēbezam bija teelaks\nGohds pahr fatweim Brahteen/\nun winna Mahte bij winna\nWahrdu Jaēbez faukusi/ fazzida-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Jaēbez peefauze\nIsraēta Deewu/ un fazzija:\ntu man ar labbu Baggatibu a\ndahwinafi/ un mannas Roh-\nschas wairofi/ un tawa Rohka\nmannim buhs/ un darrisi/\nNelatiniba mann ne apbehdiu\nUn Deews likke tam nahkt/\nwiꞥſch luhoſe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kalubs Suka Brah\ndsemdinaja Mekeru/ fchis irr\nstona Tehws.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Estons dsemdin\nBetrawu/ un Pasfeju/ un Te-\nnu/ to Tehwu ta Bilsfahta D\nas. Schee irr Reka Wihri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Keenafa Behrni\nja: Otniēls un Serajus.\nOtniēta Behrni bija Atate.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Meonotajus dse-\nnaja Owru. Un Serajus ds-\ndinaja Joabu/ to Tehwu t\nRemineschu Eeleijas/ jo tee\nRemmeschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kahleba Jiewuna D\nla Behrni bija: Irus/ Elus\nNdāms. Un Elus Behrni\nKeenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jealeēta Behrni b\nSiws un Siwus/ Tirjus\nAsareēls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Efrus Behrni b\nJeters/ un Mereds/ un Eew\nun Jalons/ un Taārs ar Mi-\nnu/ un Samaju/ un Jesbu-\nstemoq Tehwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna Seewa D\nja dsemdēja Jeredu Gedora\n"
    }
